lored beams of light to spray from your hand. Each beam has a different power. Creatures in the area of the spell with 8 HD or less are automatically blinded for 2d4 rounds. Every creature in the area is randomly struck by one or more beams, which have additional effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; frame=&quot;VOID&quot; rules=&quot;ROWS&quot;&gt;

&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;4&quot; curcol=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;b&gt;1d8&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;b&gt;Color of Beam&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;b&gt;Effect&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;4&quot; curcol=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;td&gt;1&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Red&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;20 points fire damage (Reflex half)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;
