&lt;td&gt;1st&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Stops nonmagical ranged weapons.&lt;br/&gt;
Deals 20 points of fire damage (Reflex half).&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &lt;td&gt;&lt;i&gt;Cone of cold&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;

&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr maxcol=&quot;5&quot; curcol=&quot;5&quot;&gt;
