n cast. By simply speaking aloud, you can alter reality to better suit you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Even &lt;i&gt;wish&lt;/i&gt;, however, has its limits.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;i&gt;Wish&lt;/i&gt; can produce any one of the following effects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
